            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> Genio <expan><abbr>vexillar</abbr><ex>iorum</ex></expan> et <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>imaginif</abbr><ex>erorum</ex></expan> Attianus Coresi <expan><abbr>vex</abbr><ex>illarius</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Fortionius Constitutus <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>imag</abbr><ex>inifer</ex></expan> signum cum <expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>edic</abbr><ex>u</ex><abbr>la</abbr></expan> <lb n="5"/>et tab<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>l</abbr><ex>am</ex></expan> marmoream <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ono</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ederunt</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>edicatum</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratore</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omino</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ostro</ex></expan> Gordiano <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> et Aviola co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Auf der Basis die Statuette eines opfernden Genius; Gesamthöhe: 47 cm. Die Inschrift befindet sich auf der links und rechts nach hinten abgeknickten Vorderseite der Basis.</p>
            </div>
